{"word":"G5226 - ὑπείκω - hypeíkō - hoop-i'-ko - Submit self","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὑπείκω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hypeíkō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hoop-i'-ko</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Submit self</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கீழ்ப்படி"},{"paragraph":"to yield to authority and admonition, to submit"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5259 - ὑπό - hypó - hoop-o'/5259\">G5259</a> and <b>&#x03B5;&#x03B9;&#x0313;&#x0301;&#x03BA;&#x03C9;</b> <b>eiko&#x0304;</b> (to <i>yield</i>, be &ldquo;weak&rdquo;); to <i>surrender:</i> - submit self.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}